content: In a YA novel set in a silkpunk fantasy setting, the main characters are likely to be young adults or teenagers who are coming of age and discovering their place in the world. They may be from different backgrounds, such as from a noble or peasant class, and may have unique abilities or talents. They may be on a quest to save their kingdom or village from an enemy, or may be fighting for personal freedom or to overthrow an oppressive government. They may also have to navigate through the use of advanced technology such as airships and clockwork machinery. The characters will likely have to learn to work together and rely on each other as they face challenges and overcome obstacles on their journey.
